window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>All three Toy Story novelizations in one volume! </p> <p><i>Toy Story</i> retells the classic story of the original <i>Toy Story</i> and shows just what happens when a new toy comes to town! </p> <p>In <i>Toy Story 2</i>, a toy collector steals Woody, and Buzz leads the other toys to rescue him - only to find that museum life sounds very appealing to their friend. </p> <p>Finally, in <i>Toy Story 3</i>, Andy is all grown up and heading off to college. What will happen to Buzz, Woody, and the rest of his toys? Find out in this complete retelling of the Disney/Pixar film. </p>"; 
